WEBVTT

1
00:00:23.907 --> 00:00:29.767
张穿着深色衣服，在夜间偷偷溜出房间。
Zhang, dressed in dark clothing, stealthily leaves a room at night.

2
00:00:29.767 --> 00:00:35.627
雪春走下楼梯，走进月光下的传统花园。
Xuechun descends stairs and walks into the moonlit traditional garden.

3
00:00:35.627 --> 00:00:41.487
雪春身着传统服饰，穿过月光下的花园。
Xuechun walks through the moonlit garden.

4
00:00:41.487 --> 00:00:47.350
雪春夜间若有所思地站在花园小桥旁。
Xuechun stands thoughtfully by the small garden bridge at night.

5
00:00:58.950 --> 00:01:04.795
雪春从屋里穿过拱门，步入月光下的花园。
Xuechun steps from the house into the moonlit garden through an archway.

6
00:01:04.795 --> 00:01:10.640
雪春站在门口，四处张望，然后用手比划。
Xuechun stands in the doorway, looking around, then gestures with hands.

7
00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:16.485
雪春关上门，转身扫视着黑暗的花园。
Xuechun closes the door, then turns and scans the dark garden surroundings.

8
00:01:16.485 --> 00:01:22.330
雪春独自站在黑暗的花园中，缓慢转身。
Xuechun stands alone in the dark garden, turning slowly.

9
00:01:22.330 --> 00:01:28.175
雪春走向张，张跪着遮住自己的脸。
Xuechun walks towards Zhang, who kneels and covers his face.

10
00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:39.550
雪春看着张慢慢露出脸。
Xuechun looks at Zhang as he slowly reveals his face.

11
00:01:46.850 --> 00:01:50.550
雪春为张打开了华丽的花园门。
Xuechun opens the ornate garden door for Zhang.

12
00:02:14.285 --> 00:02:16.825
张用刀刺向雪春。
Zhang stabs Xuechun with a knife.

13
00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:23.925
张培赞抬头微笑。
Zhang Peizan looks up and smiles.
